---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
import BookingButton from '../components/BookingButton.astro';
import { CircleCheckBig, MapPin, ShieldCheck, Clock, Quote } from '@lucide/astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Dr. Colin MacLeod ND"
  description="Learn about Dr. Colin MacLeod, naturopathic doctor in Halifax, Nova Scotia. Professional background, treatment philosophy and approach to naturopathic medicine."
  focusKeyword="Dr Colin MacLeod naturopathic doctor Halifax"
>
  <HeroSection title="About Dr. Colin MacLeod ND" centered compact>
    Naturopathic doctor in Bedford, Nova Scotia. Over 15 years of clinical practice.
  </HeroSection>

  <!-- Main About Content -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">

        <!-- Profile Information -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 reveal">

          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-6">The Story Behind the Practice</h2>

          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-5 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Dr. Colin MacLeod grew up in Judique, a small community on the western shore of Cape Breton Island. At 18, a serious bout of mononucleosis prevented him from finishing his final year of high school. He saw doctor after doctor without a clear diagnosis or a treatment that made any real difference. It was a frustrating and isolating experience. Then a naturopathic doctor entered the picture. The approach was different: thorough, unhurried, and genuinely curious about the whole person. It worked. That experience didn't just restore his health; it pointed his life in a new direction.
          </p>

          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
            He went on to complete prerequisite studies in biology at Saint Mary's University in Halifax and the University of Calgary, then earned his Doctor of Naturopathic Medicine from the Canadian College of Naturopathic Medicine in Toronto, a rigorous four-year clinical program and one of the most respected naturopathic programs in North America.
          </p>

          <!-- Career narrative -->
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-5 leading-relaxed">
            After graduating from CCNM, Dr. MacLeod returned to Nova Scotia and spent six years building clinical experience working with patients across the Halifax Regional Municipality. He then took the step of establishing his own independent practice in Tantallon (MacLeod Naturopathic Health Clinic), which he ran for seven years.
          </p>

          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
            Throughout much of that period, he also maintained a part-time practice in Cape Breton, first in Port Hood and then in Sydney, returning regularly to serve the communities that raised him. The people there are, in his words, just incredible. He kept it up for nearly a decade, until the arrival of his second son made the travel impractical. Today, Dr. MacLeod practices out of Optimal Wellbeing Clinic on the Bedford Highway in Bedford, alongside fellow health professionals.
          </p>

          <!-- Pain philosophy pull quote -->
          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-emerald-600 bg-emerald-50 rounded-r-2xl px-6 py-5 my-8">
            <p class="text-emerald-900 italic text-lg leading-relaxed">"Physical pain is a unique equalizer. We can all be as mentally tough as we want, but pain levels the playing field. You can't be tough enough to overcome pain that limits your daily life. Understanding that is what drew me to prolotherapy: it doesn't just manage the pain, it addresses the underlying damage driving it."</p>
            <cite class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700 mt-3 block not-italic">Dr. Colin MacLeod ND</cite>
          </blockquote>

          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
            IV nutrient therapy is another treatment Dr. MacLeod is particularly passionate about, and one he has experienced firsthand. The revitalizing effects of IV magnesium, vitamin C and B vitamins are, in his words, a genuine leg up for patients who are running on empty. When the body is depleted by chronic illness, persistent stress or poor absorption, IV delivery can correct deficiencies in a way that oral supplementation simply cannot match. Better energy, clearer thinking, improved immune resilience: results like these can open a window that allows patients to make real progress.
          </p>

          <!-- Education & Training -->
          <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-4">Education & Training</h3>
          <div class="bg-emerald-50/30 border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-8">
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <CircleCheckBig class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-800 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" />
                <span class="text-gray-700">Doctor of Naturopathic Medicine (ND), Canadian College of Naturopathic Medicine, Toronto</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <CircleCheckBig class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" />
                <span class="text-gray-700">Prerequisite studies in biology, Saint Mary's University (Halifax) and University of Calgary</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <CircleCheckBig class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" />
                <span class="text-gray-700">Licensed to practice naturopathic medicine in Nova Scotia</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <CircleCheckBig class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" />
                <span class="text-gray-700">Advanced training in prolotherapy and regenerative injection therapies</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <CircleCheckBig class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" />
                <span class="text-gray-700">Certified in intravenous therapy</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Treatment Philosophy -->
          <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-4">Treatment Philosophy</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Dr. MacLeod's approach is rooted in the naturopathic principle of finding and treating the underlying cause, not just managing symptoms. He builds individualized treatment plans that combine the best of traditional wisdom with current scientific evidence, and he works collaboratively with each patient's existing healthcare team rather than in isolation from it.
          </p>


        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <div class="space-y-8 reveal reveal-delay-200 order-first lg:order-none">

          <!-- Doctor Photo -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <img
              src="/images/general/dr-colin-macleod-nd.webp"
              alt="Dr. Colin MacLeod ND - Naturopathic Doctor Bedford NS"
              class="w-full aspect-[3/4] object-cover object-top"
              width="600"
              height="800"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Quick Facts -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-4">Professional Details</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <MapPin class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-800 mr-3" aria-hidden="true" />
                <span class="text-gray-700">Bedford, Nova Scotia</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <ShieldCheck class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 mr-3" aria-hidden="true" />
                <span class="text-gray-700">Licensed ND in Nova Scotia</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <Clock class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 mr-3" aria-hidden="true" />
                <span class="text-gray-700">15 Years of Clinical Experience</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Insurance -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-3">Insurance & Billing</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">Most extended health plans cover naturopathic visits. Direct billing is available for many major insurers including Sun Life, Great-West Life, Manulife and Blue Cross.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Specializations -->
          <div class="bg-emerald-50/50 border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-4">Clinical Focus</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Chronic Pain Management
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Musculoskeletal Injuries
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                IV Nutrient Therapy
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Regenerative Medicine
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Fatigue & Energy Disorders
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Digestive Health
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Stress & Sleep Disorders
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Marathon Running -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-4 text-center reveal">Beyond the Clinic</h2>
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10 mt-6 flex gap-4 reveal reveal-delay-100">
          <Quote class="w-10 h-10 text-emerald-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true" />
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
            <span class="italic">I started running in 2023, completing my first 10K that May. I enjoy setting running goals for myself and I'm gradually learning what it takes to achieve them. The physical and mental benefits of exercise are truly amazing. I hope to keep active and continue running for many years to come.</span> <span class="font-medium text-gray-700 ml-8">&ndash; Dr. Colin</span>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center reveal reveal-delay-200">
          <!-- Image -->
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <img
              src="/images/general/bluenose-marathon.webp"
              alt="Dr. Colin MacLeod running the Bluenose Marathon in Halifax"
              class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
              width="800"
              height="600"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Results Table -->
          <div class="bg-emerald-50/30 border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden h-fit">
            <div class="px-6 py-4 bg-emerald-100/50 border-b border-emerald-100">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-emerald-950">Race Results</h3>
            </div>
            <table class="w-full">
              <thead>
                <tr class="border-b border-emerald-100">
                  <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-900">Year</th>
                  <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-900">Event</th>
                  <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-900">Finish Time</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="divide-y divide-emerald-50">
                <tr>
                  <td class="px-4 py-4 text-gray-700">2024</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-4 text-gray-700">Bluenose Marathon</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-4 text-gray-700 font-medium">3:57:14</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="px-4 py-4 text-gray-700">2025</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-4 text-gray-700">Bluenose Marathon</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-4 text-gray-700 font-medium">4:21:21</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="bg-emerald-50/50">
                  <td class="px-4 py-4 text-gray-700">2026</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-4 text-gray-700">Bluenose Marathon</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-4 text-gray-700 font-medium italic">In Training</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact CTA -->
  <section class="bg-emerald-950 py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="section-shell text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-6">Ready to Begin Your Health Journey?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-white/90 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Dr. MacLeod is accepting new patients. Visit the <a href="/new-patients" class="text-emerald-300 hover:text-white underline underline-offset-2 transition-colors">New Patients page</a> to learn what to expect and what to bring to your first appointment.
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <BookingButton text="Book Online" source="about-cta" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>